<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #292648;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 24px;
            background-color: #292648;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: none;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #3a3769;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to School ERP</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p>Welcome to School ERP! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p>Your account has been successfully created. You can now access all the features of our platform.</p>
        <p>To get started, please click the button below to log in to your account:</p>
        
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button" style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;">Login to Your Account</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>School ERP Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 School ERP. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 